                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-95532199" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="95532199">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/XIAOWANYI1108/">小玩意</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2009-02-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">看不懂，但这个版本印刷排版不咋地。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="370175034">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-370175034" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-370175034" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="370175034">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leftonye/">LEFTON</a>
                    <span>2011-03-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实都是在用一些形象的东西（相）进行教导，像是本童话书（其实童话里都各有玄机，偶然听过一则便觉汗毛竖起 ..），更像是闭卷考前露答案的书一定要背牢了啊，似乎懂点但深度有多少值得怀疑而且并不觉认同，需要刹那间的机缘，而机缘是有人点的或是主动找老师或是自己偶然感受到的</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="425768999">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-425768999" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-425768999" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="425768999">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1747161/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-10-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">非针对普通读者，不如《西藏生死书》亲切。但其中可挖掘的东西很多，对荣格的引用也极有启发意义。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

